      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=kdcxt0r0tg]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=kdcxt0r0tg]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=wq7twvfkft]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=wq7twvfkft]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pz6119ames]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pz6119ames]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=foe7dcvso1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=foe7dcvso1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n5thyy255j]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n5thyy255j]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=p3z6cbmxzq]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=p3z6cbmxzq]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jwc8nvabva]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jwc8nvabva]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=j2aa4gpo8r]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=j2aa4gpo8r]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=nlq04w1l0b]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nlq04w1l0b]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=vt1brm661i]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vt1brm661i]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=c61weujz87]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=c61weujz87]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=y6cc51h3n0]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y6cc51h3n0]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=rh2u905yej]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=rh2u905yej]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759727278137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759727278137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"620462405\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shading_learingPath_banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"92550578-e31b-4fee-8a4c-09f87623804a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759727278137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=640 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/shading_learingPath_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1759727278137&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320 1x\" /></span><p /><p>The Shading learning path is for artists who are keen to enhance their shading skills, whether using PxrSurface or MaterialX Lama.  We will also take a look at using and controlling textures with RenderMan through to procedural shading workflows</p><h1 id=\"ShadingPath-StartHere\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"wq7twvfkft\">Start Here</span></strong></h1><p>If you&rsquo;re new to shading in RenderMan, here&rsquo;s a good place to start</p><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599163179/PxrSurface\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599163179\" data-linked-resource-version=\"33\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaPlastic.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaPlastic.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208606365&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/LamaPlastic.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208606365&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607027250\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaPlastic.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"e44bfeac-c88f-4db8-968e-aa9d84073304\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaPlastic.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208606365&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaPlastic.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208606365&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"nlq04w1l0b\">PxrSurface Basics</span></strong><br />The PxrSurface is the creative heart of shading at Pixar.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599654499/MaterialX+Lama\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599654499\" data-linked-resource-version=\"43\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaMetal.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaMetal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208586492&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/LamaMetal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208586492&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606928954\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaMetal.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"7699c608-0c13-440c-a484-b16399737362\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaMetal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208586492&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaMetal.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758208586492&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"jwc8nvabva\">Lama Basics</span></strong><br />Thanks to ILM, you can learn their layered shading system</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"ShadingPath-NextSteps\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"y6cc51h3n0\">Next Steps</span></strong></h1><p>Now that you&rsquo;ve learned the basics of how materials work in RenderMan, the following steps build upon the fundamental lessons<strong><span data-colorid=\"j2aa4gpo8r\">.</span></strong></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599883858/Textures\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599883858\" data-linked-resource-version=\"46\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaFundamentals.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758208613455&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758208613455&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606994502\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaFundamentals.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"9c7463f2-f5d1-48e6-b194-5896c61ec128\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758208613455&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/LamaFundamentals.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758208613455&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"pz6119ames\">Textures</span></strong><br />Learn how to control textures within your shading networks.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/599163195/Procedural\" data-linked-resource-id=\"599163195\" data-linked-resource-version=\"27\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"proceduralThumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/proceduralThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760013068497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/proceduralThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760013068497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"606765128\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"proceduralThumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"8242a9c0-4758-451c-82ca-94e0db80886b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/proceduralThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760013068497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/proceduralThumb.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1760013068497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"p3z6cbmxzq\">Procedural Shading</span></strong><br />Learn the basics of procedural shading. </p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"ComingSoon_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/ComingSoon_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762501479495&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/ComingSoon_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762501479495&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"500\" data-width=\"500\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"654671905\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ComingSoon_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"fab789b1-52ba-4516-93d1-a32f2f39bde5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/ComingSoon_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762501479495&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=500&amp;height=500 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/ComingSoon_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762501479495&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"c61weujz87\"> Bump &amp; Displacement</span></strong></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"ShadingPath-PracticalExamples\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"n5thyy255j\">Practical Examples</span></strong></h1></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"CupCakeTutorial.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/CupCakeTutorial.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759318558136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=260\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163154/CupCakeTutorial.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759318558136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1194\" data-width=\"1195\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"616333315\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"CupCakeTutorial.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163154\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"43\" data-media-id=\"d01da581-7718-487e-950f-8588eb58746c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/CupCakeTutorial.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759318558136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=520 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163154/CupCakeTutorial.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759318558136&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=260 1x\" /></span><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"vt1brm661i\">Shading a cupcake</span></strong><br />Pixar University presents its Shading Onboarding Lesson!</p><p>Coming Soon!</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" dat